<article id="post-277" class="post-277 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry">
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">The Chicago Social Justice Lens Film Series</h1>		<div class="breadcrumbs">
					</div>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9c0e0e;"><strong>Debt, Economic Justice, and Racial Divides: What&#8217;s the Connection? </strong></span><span style="color: #9c0e0e;"><strong> </strong></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="wp-image-1097 aligncenter" src="http://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-1024x511.png" alt="" width="1051" height="524" srcset="https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-1024x511.png 1024w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-300x150.png 300w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-768x384.png 768w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-250x125.png 250w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-550x275.png 550w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-800x400.png 800w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-360x180.png 360w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-601x300.png 601w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-1001x500.png 1001w, https://sji.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Screen-Shot-2018-09-04-at-5.40.09-PM-wecompress.com_-400x200.png 400w" sizes="(max-width: 1051px) 100vw, 1051px" /></p>
<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="65r8m" data-offset-key="4imj0-0-0">
<h3 data-offset-key="4imj0-0-0"></h3>
<h3 class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="4imj0-0-0">Public debt has increased sharply in many countries in recent years, particularly during and after the Great Recession. The US alone holds almost a third of the world&#8217;s total debt.  Debt, Economic Justice and Racial Divides: What&#8217;s the Connection? is the 4th annual documentary film series hosted by the Social Justice Initiative.</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>This year&#8217;s film series explores the national and international challenges of these dire economic conditions. Each film shares a unique perspective on how communities are impacted and why indebtedness has shaped the financial future of millions around the world. Post-film discussions to follow each screening.</h3>
</div>
<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="65r8m" data-offset-key="1c6ig-0-0"></div>
<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="65r8m" data-offset-key="d7lh6-0-0">
<div class="_1mf _1mj" style="text-align: center;" data-offset-key="d7lh6-0-0"></div>
</div>
<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="65r8m" data-offset-key="6eskc-0-0">
<div class="_1mf _1mj" data-offset-key="6eskc-0-0"><span data-offset-key="6eskc-0-0"> </span></div>
</div>
<div class="" data-block="true" data-editor="65r8m" data-offset-key="a09kl-0-0"></div>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">SPACE IS LIMITED &#8211; <a href="http://www.sjifilms.eventbrite.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #ff9900;">TICKET REQUIRED!</span></a></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://sji2018films.eventbrite.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here</a> to RSVP Today</h3>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://Sji2018films.eventbrite.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sji2018films.eventbrite.com</a></span></h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">&#8212;&#8211;</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff9900;"><strong>Life &amp; Debt</strong></span></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9e0e0e;"><strong>September 13, 2018 </strong></span></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9e0e0e;"> Pop-Up JUST Art Gallery| 1344 S. Halsted St.</span><br />
<span style="color: #ff9900;">RSVP: </span><a href="https://sjifilm1.eventbrite.com">https://sjifilm1.eventbrite.com</a></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">Based on the book &#8220;A Small Place&#8221; by Jamaica Kincaid, the film Life &amp; Debt focuses on the stories of individual Jamaicans whose precarious day-to-day existence are determined by the agendas of U.S. and other foreign economic forces.</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ff9900;">Default: The Student Loan Documentary</span></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9c0e0e;"><strong>September 12, 2017 </strong></span></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9c0e0e;"><strong>Student Center East | 750 S. Halsted St.</strong></span></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">This film chronicles the stories of borrowers from different backgrounds affected by the student lending industry and their struggles to change the system. The dire student loan consequences are highlighted by the stories of borrowers in financial and emotional ruin.</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><span style="color: #ff9900;">The Debt of Dictators </span></span></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 1rem;"><span style="color: #ff9900;"><span style="color: #9c0e0e;">September 25, 2018 </span></span></span></h3>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #9e0e0e;">Pop-Up JUST Art Gallery| 1344 S. Halsted St.</span></h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;">The Debt of Dictators explores how the lending of billions of dollars by multinational banks and international financial institutions to dictators from three third-world countries impacts the health, education, and welfare of it’s citizens.</h4>
<h4 style="text-align: center;"></h4>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

